#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h2>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:4
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus is a proud member of the Commonhaus Foundation"
msgstr "クオークスはコモンハウス財団の会員です。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:7
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Commonhaus Foundation which is a non-profit dedicated to the enduring viability of open-source projects. It offers a neutral environment, a governing structure, and assistance to projects, prioritizing their independence and development led by the community. They furnish resources such as legal aid, infrastructure, and financial avenues, all while honoring each project's established governance and culture."
msgstr "Commonhaus Foundationは、オープンソースプロジェクトの永続的な存続を目的とした非営利団体です。中立的な環境、運営体制、プロジェクトへの支援を提供し、プロジェクトの独立性とコミュニティ主導の開発を優先します。各プロジェクトの確立されたガバナンスと文化を尊重しつつ、法的支援、インフラ、資金調達手段などのリソースを提供します。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:8
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.commonhaus.org/\" target=\"blank\">Learn more about the Commonhaus Foundation and how you can make a difference</a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://www.commonhaus.org/\" target=\"blank\">コモンハウス財団の詳細と、どのように変化をもたらすことができるかについては、こちらをご覧ください。</a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><a>
#: _includes/benefactors.html:11
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a href=\"https://www.commonhaus.org/\" target=\"blank\">"
msgstr "<a href=\"https://www.commonhaus.org/\" target=\"blank\">"

